You dont annoy me.
You can actually buy me a beer in NoLa and I will teach you some Nirvana facts.

@ManniMD1 Her brother (my uncle) has MGUS.
He is ok with Just waiting. 

With this family history, I know my odds. I will tell you how I handle it if/when it happens.

@ManniMD1 Just a personal history.
My favourite aunt has high risk SMM. She asks me constantly if all she could do is wait for the disease to evolve. She is really smart and reads a lot about MM.

She Just cant handle being passive about it.

@ManniMD1 Let me correct you.

"Should they be offered the opportunity of consenting to participate in a trial".

Enrollment is not a passive action. People are not treated without knowing the risks/possible benefits.

